title: Waffles
instructions: Preheat your waffle maker.
In a mixing bowl, combine waffle mix, eggs, milk, and oil according to the package instructions.
Pour the batter into the preheated waffle maker.
Cook until the waffle is golden brown and crispy.
Carefully remove the waffle and serve with your favorite toppings.

title: Pancakes
instructions: Preheat your griddle to medium heat.
In a mixing bowl, whisk together pancake mix, eggs, milk, and oil according to the package instructions.
Pour batter onto the griddle to form pancakes.
Cook until bubbles form on the surface, then flip and cook until golden brown on the other side.
Serve with butter and syrup.

title: Scrambled Eggs
instructions: Crack eggs into a bowl and whisk until smooth.
Heat a frying pan over medium heat and add butter.
Pour the eggs into the pan and let them set for a few seconds.
Gently stir the eggs with a spatula, pushing them from the edges to the center.
Cook until the eggs are just set but still soft, then remove from the pan and serve.

title: Grilled Cheese Sandwich
instructions: Butter one side of each slice of bread.
Place one slice, buttered side down, in a preheated skillet.
Add cheese slices on top of the bread.
Place the second slice of bread on top, buttered side up.
Cook until the bread is golden brown and the cheese is melted, flipping once.
Remove from skillet, slice, and serve.

title: Spaghetti Aglio e Olio
instructions: Cook spaghetti according to package instructions until al dente.
While the pasta cooks, heat olive oil in a skillet over medium heat.
Add sliced garlic and red pepper flakes to the skillet and sauté until the garlic is golden.
Drain the pasta, reserving some pasta water.
Toss the pasta with the garlic and oil mixture, adding a little pasta water if needed.
Season with salt and serve with a sprinkle of parsley.

title: Caesar Salad
instructions: In a salad bowl, combine chopped romaine lettuce with Caesar dressing.
Toss until the lettuce is well coated.
Add croutons and grated Parmesan cheese.
Toss again to distribute the toppings evenly.
Serve immediately.
